  "textPreview": "My day trading setup\n我的当日交易设置\nDecember 20, 2020 By Al Brooks\n2020 年 12 月 20 日 作者：阿尔·布鲁克斯\n发帖\nAlthough it might be hard to believe, my day trading setup uses only a single 13″\nlaptop for my trading. It has my charts and a trading platform from one or two\nbrokers. A trader does not need any more than this to make money. Just print out a\n5-minute chart of any market at the end of the day and you will see many trades.\nWith experience, you might see potential trades on almost every bar on the chart!\n尽管可能难以置信，但我的日间交易设置仅使用一台 13 英寸笔记本电脑进行交易。它有我的图\n表和一两个经纪人的交易平台。交易者不需要更多的东西就能赚钱。只要在当天结束时打印出任\n何市场的 5 分钟图表，您就会看到许多交易。凭借经验，您可能会在图表上的几乎每个柱上看到\n潜在的交易！\nMy chart for day trading the 5-minute Emini has two exponential moving averages (EMAs), each based\non 20 bars. The solid blue line is the 20-bar EMA of the 5-minute chart. The dashed line is the EMA of\nthe 20-bar EMA from the 60-minute chart, but I wrote the indicator in a way that allows me to plot it on\nthe 5-minute chart (I put the TradeStation EasyLanguage code below).\n我的 5 分钟 Emini 日内交易图表有两个指数移动平均线 (EMA)，每个均线基于 20 个柱。蓝色实\n线是 5 分钟图表的 20 条 EMA。虚线是 60 分钟图表中 20 根 EMA 的 EMA，但我编写该指标的方\n式允许我将其绘制在 5 分钟图表上（我将 TradeStation EasyLanguage 代码放在下面）。\nOnly need one chart\n只需要一张图表\nDuring 99% of the day, I am looking at a single 5-minute chart, which is usually the\nEmini, but I also sometimes trade Forex markets, bond futures, crude oil, natural\ngas, stocks, and options. I sometimes look at 60-minute, daily, weekly, and\nmonthly charts.\n一天中 99% 的时间里，我都在看一张 5 分钟图表，通常是 Emini，但有时我也会交易外汇市\n场、债券期货、原油、天然气、股票和期权。我有时会查看 60 分钟、日线、周线和月线图表。\nBrooks Trading Course 布鲁克斯交易课程\nSign ",
